2026-01-08 18:23:48;Mai Quá»³nh Anh;"import json
import os

# ==========================================
# 1. DATA LOADER & UTILS
# ==========================================
class DataLoader:
    def __init__(self, data_dir='.'):
        self.data_dir = data_dir

    def load_json(self, filename):
        path = os.path.join(self.data_dir, filename)
        if not os.path.exists(path):
            print(f""âš ï¸ Cáº£nh bÃ¡o: KhÃ´ng tÃ¬m tháº¥y file {filename}"")
            return [] if filename == 'courses.json' else {}
        with open(path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:
            return json.load(f)

    def get_student_status(self, localstorage_data):
        """"""PhÃ¢n loáº¡i mÃ´n: ÄÃ£ qua, Rá»›t, Äang há»c""""""
        passed = set()
        failed = set()
        studying = set()
        
        grades = localstorage_data.get('student_db_full', {}).get('grades', [])
        for g in grades:
            cid = g.get('id')
            score_raw = g.get('score')
            
            # Logic Ä‘iá»ƒm sá»‘: Rá»—ng hoáº·c (*) lÃ  Ä‘ang há»c
            if score_raw == """" or score_raw == ""(*)"" or score_raw is None:
                studying.add(cid)
                continue
            
            try:
                score = float(score_raw)
                if score >= 5.0:
                    passed.add(cid)
                else:
                    failed.add(cid)
            except:
                studying.add(cid)
                
        return passed, failed, studying

# ==========================================
# 2. GRAPH ENGINE (Xá»¬ LÃ TIÃŠN QUYáº¾T)
# ==========================================
class PrerequisiteGraph:
    def __init__(self, prereq_data):
        self.hard_constraints = {} # TiÃªn quyáº¿t (Báº¯t buá»™c)
        self.soft_constraints = {} # Há»c trÆ°á»›c (Khuyáº¿n khÃ­ch)
        self.build_graph(prereq_data)

    def build_graph(self, data):
        for item in data:
            c_id = item['course_id']
            p_id = item['prereq_id']
            p_type = item.get('type', 'PREREQUISITE')
            
            if p_type == 'PREREQUISITE':
                if c_id not in self.hard_constraints: self.hard_constraints[c_id] = []
                self.hard_constraints[c_id].append(p_id)
            elif p_type == 'PREVIOUS':
                if c_id not in self.soft_constraints: self.soft_constraints[c_id] = []
                self.soft_constraints[c_id].append(p_id)

    def find_blocking_prereq(self, course_id, passed_courses):
        """"""
        Äá»‡ quy tÃ¬m mÃ´n 'gá»‘c' nháº¥t cáº§n há»c.
        Náº¿u mÃ´n A cáº§n B, B chÆ°a há»c -> Check B.
        Náº¿u B cáº§n C, C chÆ°a há»c -> Tráº£ vá» C.
        """"""
        # Náº¿u mÃ´n nÃ y Ä‘Ã£ há»c rá»“i -> KhÃ´ng cáº§n há»c ná»¯a (Base case)
        if course_id in passed_courses:
            return None

        # Láº¥y danh sÃ¡ch tiÃªn quyáº¿t cá»©ng cá»§a mÃ´n nÃ y
        reqs = self.hard_constraints.get(course_id, [])
        
        for req in reqs:
            if req not in passed_courses:
                # Äá»‡ quy: Kiá»ƒm tra xem mÃ´n tiÃªn quyáº¿t 'req' cÃ³ bá»‹ cháº·n bá»Ÿi ai khÃ¡c khÃ´ng
                deeper_blocker = self.find_blocking_prereq(req, passed_courses)
                if deeper_blocker:
                    return deeper_blocker
                else:
                    # Náº¿u 'req' khÃ´ng bá»‹ ai cháº·n, thÃ¬ chÃ­nh 'req' lÃ  mÃ´n cáº§n há»c ngay
                    return req
        
        # Náº¿u khÃ´ng cÃ³ tiÃªn quyáº¿t nÃ o chÆ°a há»c, thÃ¬ chÃ­nh course_id lÃ  mÃ´n cÃ³ thá»ƒ há»c
        return course_id

# ==========================================
# 3. CORE RECOMMENDER (LOGIC CHÃNH)
# ==========================================
class CourseRecommender:
    def __init__(self):
        self.loader = DataLoader()
        self.MAX_CREDITS = 25 # Giá»›i háº¡n tÃ­n chá»‰ tá»‘i Ä‘a

    def run(self):
        # --- LOAD DATA ---
        courses_meta = self.loader.load_json('courses.json') # List
        courses_map = {c['course_id']: c for c in courses_meta} # Dict Ä‘á»ƒ tra cá»©u nhanh
        
        prereqs = self.loader.load_json('prerequisites.json')
        local_data = self.loader.load_json('localstorage.json')
        
        # Láº¥y danh sÃ¡ch lá»›p má»Ÿ (Schedule)
        open_classes_raw = local_data.get('courses_db_offline', [])
        # Map ID lá»›p má»Ÿ -> Data chi tiáº¿t lá»›p má»Ÿ
        open_classes_map = {c['id']: c for c in open_classes_raw}

        # --- STEP 1: PHÃ‚N TÃCH NGÆ¯á»œI DÃ™NG ---
        passed, failed, studying = self.loader.get_student_status(local_data)
        graph = PrerequisiteGraph(prereqs)
        
        raw_list = set() # DÃ¹ng set Ä‘á»ƒ trÃ¡nh trÃ¹ng láº·p

        # --- STEP 2: Xá»¬ LÃ MÃ”N Ná»¢ (Æ¯U TIÃŠN 1) ---
        print(f""ğŸ” TÃ¬m mÃ´n ná»£..."")
        for cid in failed:
            # Check Ä‘á»‡ quy tiÃªn quyáº¿t cho mÃ´n ná»£ (Ä‘á» phÃ²ng quy cháº¿ Ä‘á»•i)
            target = graph.find_blocking_prereq(cid, passed)
            if target:
                raw_list.add(target)

        # --- STEP 3: Xá»¬ LÃ MÃ”N Báº®T BUá»˜C (Æ¯U TIÃŠN 2) ---
        print(f""ğŸ” TÃ¬m mÃ´n báº¯t buá»™c chÆ°a há»c..."")
        for c in courses_meta:
            cid = c['course_id']
            # Äiá»u kiá»‡n: LÃ  mÃ´n Báº¯t buá»™c (BB) VÃ€ ChÆ°a qua VÃ€ KhÃ´ng Ä‘ang há»c
            if c.get('course_type') == 'BB' and cid not in passed and cid not in studying:
                # Äá»‡ quy tÃ¬m mÃ´n tiÃªn quyáº¿t gáº§n nháº¥t
                target = graph.find_blocking_prereq(cid, passed)
                if target and target not in passed and target not in studying:
                    raw_list.add(target)

        # --- STEP 4: Xá»¬ LÃ MÃ”N Há»ŒC TRÆ¯á»šC (Æ¯U TIÃŠN 3 - CHECK TÃN CHá»ˆ) ---
        # TÃ­nh tÃ­n chá»‰ hiá»‡n táº¡i cá»§a raw_list
        current_credits = 0
        for cid in raw_list:
            if cid in courses_map:
                current_credits += courses_map[cid].get('credits', 0)

        print(f""â„¹ï¸ TÃ­n chá»‰ báº¯t buá»™c/ná»£ dá»± kiáº¿n: {current_credits}"")
        
        if current_credits < self.MAX_CREDITS:
            print(f""ğŸ” Äá» xuáº¥t thÃªm mÃ´n 'Há»c trÆ°á»›c' (Soft Prereq)..."")
            soft_candidates = set()
            
            # Duyá»‡t cÃ¡c mÃ´n trong raw_list Ä‘á»ƒ xem cÃ³ mÃ´n nÃ o nÃªn há»c bá»• trá»£ khÃ´ng
            # Hoáº·c duyá»‡t cÃ¡c mÃ´n tá»± chá»n (TC) chÆ°a há»c
            # á» Ä‘Ã¢y mÃ¬nh demo logic: Láº¥y mÃ´n 'Previous' cá»§a cÃ¡c mÃ´n trong raw_list
            for cid in list(raw_list): # Convert list Ä‘á»ƒ duyá»‡t an toÃ n
                prevs = graph.soft_constraints.get(cid, [])
                for p in prevs:
                    if p not in passed and p not in raw_list and p not in studying:
                        # Kiá»ƒm tra xem mÃ´n Previous nÃ y cÃ³ Ä‘á»§ Ä‘iá»u kiá»‡n há»c khÃ´ng
                        valid_p = graph.find_blocking_prereq(p, passed)
                        if valid_p == p: # Chá»‰ add náº¿u chÃ­nh nÃ³ há»c Ä‘Æ°á»£c ngay
                            soft_candidates.add(p)
            
            # Add vÃ o raw_list náº¿u cÃ²n slot tÃ­n chá»‰
            for sc in soft_candidates:
                c_cred = courses_map.get(sc, {}).get('credits', 0)
                if current_credits + c_cred <= self.MAX_CREDITS:
                    raw_list.add(sc)
                    current_credits += c_cred

        # --- STEP 5: FINAL FILTER (CHECK Lá»ŠCH Lá»šP Má») ---
        print(f""ğŸ” Kiá»ƒm tra lá»‹ch má»Ÿ lá»›p (Offline DB)..."")
        final_output = []
        
        # Convert set -> list Ä‘á»ƒ sort (Æ°u tiÃªn hiá»ƒn thá»‹)
        sorted_candidates = sorted(list(raw_list))

        for cid in sorted_candidates:
            # Kiem tra xem mon nay co trong danh sach lop mo khong
            if cid in open_classes_map:
                # Láº¥y Ä‘Ãºng format trong localstorage (bao gá»“m schedules)
                class_info = open_classes_map[cid]
                final_output.append(class_info)
            else:
                # Log debug náº¿u muá»‘n biáº¿t mÃ´n nÃ o cáº§n há»c nhÆ°ng trÆ°á»ng khÃ´ng má»Ÿ
                # print(f""   Skipped {cid}: TrÆ°á»ng khÃ´ng má»Ÿ lá»›p ká»³ nÃ y."")
                pass

        return final_output

# ==========================================
# 4. EXECUTION
# ==========================================
if __name__ == ""__main__"":
    app = CourseRecommender()
    result = app.run()
    
    # Xuáº¥t káº¿t quáº£

    with open(output_filename, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:

2026-01-08 18:38:09;Mai Quá»³nh Anh;=)))
2026-01-08 18:38:49;Mai Quá»³nh Anh;"const fs = require('fs');
const path = require('path');

// ==========================================
// 1. DATA LOADER (Äá»ŒC Dá»® LIá»†U)
// ==========================================
class DataLoader {
    constructor(dataDir = '.') {
        this.dataDir = dataDir;
    }

    loadJson(filename) {
        const filePath = path.join(this.dataDir, filename);
        if (!fs.existsSync(filePath)) {
            console.warn(`âš ï¸ Cáº£nh bÃ¡o: KhÃ´ng tÃ¬m tháº¥y file ${filename}`);
            return filename === 'courses.json' ? [] : {};
        }
        const rawData = fs.readFileSync(filePath, 'utf-8');
        return JSON.parse(rawData);
    }

    getStudentStatus(localData) {
        const passed = new Set();
        const failed = new Set();
        const studying = new Set();

        // Safe access (Optional chaining)
        const grades = localData?.student_db_full?.grades || [];

        grades.forEach(g => {
            const cid = g.id;
            let scoreRaw = g.score;

            // Xá»­ lÃ½ cÃ¡c trÆ°á»ng há»£p Ä‘ang há»c: rá»—ng, null, hoáº·c ""(*)""
            if (scoreRaw === """" || scoreRaw === ""(*)"" || scoreRaw === null || scoreRaw === undefined) {
                studying.add(cid);
                return;
            }

            // Ã‰p kiá»ƒu sang sá»‘
            const score = parseFloat(scoreRaw);
            if (!isNaN(score)) {
                if (score >= 5.0) {
                    passed.add(cid);
                } else {
                    failed.add(cid);
                }
            } else {
                // TrÆ°á»ng há»£p Ä‘iá»ƒm tÃ o lao, coi nhÆ° Ä‘ang há»c
                studying.add(cid);
            }
        });

        return { passed, failed, studying };
    }
}

// ==========================================
// 2. GRAPH ENGINE (Xá»¬ LÃ CÃ‚Y TIÃŠN QUYáº¾T)
// ==========================================
class PrerequisiteGraph {
    constructor(prereqData) {
        this.hardConstraints = {}; // Báº¯t buá»™c (PREREQUISITE)
        this.softConstraints = {}; // Khuyáº¿n khÃ­ch (PREVIOUS)
        this.buildGraph(prereqData);
    }

    buildGraph(data) {
        data.forEach(item => {
            const cId = item.course_id;
            const pIdRaw = item.prereq_id;
            const type = item.type || 'PREREQUISITE';

            // Xá»­ lÃ½ trÆ°á»ng há»£p 1 Ã´ chá»©a nhiá»u mÃ£: ""CSC10001, CSC10002""
            // Thay tháº¿ dáº¥u pháº©y báº±ng khoáº£ng tráº¯ng rá»“i split
            const pIds = pIdRaw.replace(/,/g, ' ').split(/\s+/).filter(x => x.length > 0);

            pIds.forEach(pid => {
                if (type === 'PREREQUISITE') {
                    if (!this.hardConstraints[cId]) this.hardConstraints[cId] = [];
                    this.hardConstraints[cId].push(pid);
                } else if (type === 'PREVIOUS') {
                    if (!this.softConstraints[cId]) this.softConstraints[cId] = [];
                    this.softConstraints[cId].push(pid);
                }
            });
        });
    }

    /**
     * Äá»‡ quy tÃ¬m mÃ´n ""Gá»‘c"" cáº§n há»c.
     * @param {string} courseId - MÃ´n Ä‘Ã­ch muá»‘n há»c
     * @param {Set} passedCourses - Danh sÃ¡ch mÃ´n Ä‘Ã£ qua
     * @returns {string|null} - Tráº£ vá» null náº¿u mÃ´n Ä‘Ã­ch Ä‘Ã£ há»c rá»“i.
     * Tráº£ vá» courseId náº¿u Ä‘á»§ Ä‘iá»u kiá»‡n há»c.
     * Tráº£ vá» mÃ´n tiÃªn quyáº¿t náº¿u bá»‹ cháº·n.
     */
    findBlockingPrereq(courseId, passedCourses) {
        // Base case: Náº¿u mÃ´n nÃ y Ä‘Ã£ há»c rá»“i -> ThÃ´i, khÃ´ng cáº§n há»c ná»¯a
        if (passedCourses.has(courseId)) {
            return null;
        }

        const reqs = this.hardConstraints[courseId] || [];

        for (const req of reqs) {
            // Náº¿u mÃ´n tiÃªn quyáº¿t chÆ°a há»c
            if (!passedCourses.has(req)) {
                // Äá»‡ quy sÃ¢u hÆ¡n: Xem tháº±ng tiÃªn quyáº¿t Ä‘Ã³ cÃ³ bá»‹ ai cháº·n khÃ´ng?
                const deeperBlocker = this.findBlockingPrereq(req, passedCourses);

                if (deeperBlocker) {
                    return deeperBlocker; // Tráº£ vá» Ã´ng tá»• bá»‹ cháº·n
                } else {
                    return req; // ChÃ­nh tháº±ng req nÃ y lÃ  váº­t cáº£n
                }
            }
        }

        // Náº¿u khÃ´ng cÃ³ tiÃªn quyáº¿t nÃ o cáº£n trá»Ÿ -> Há»c Ä‘Æ°á»£c mÃ´n nÃ y
        return courseId;
    }
}

// ==========================================
// 3. CORE RECOMMENDER (LOGIC CHÃNH)
// ==========================================
class CourseRecommender {
    constructor() {
        this.loader = new DataLoader();
    }

    run() {
        console.log(""â³ Äang xá»­ lÃ½ dá»¯ liá»‡u..."");

        // 1. Load Data
        const coursesMeta = this.loader.loadJson('courses.json');
        const prereqs = this.loader.loadJson('prerequisites.json');
        const localData = this.loader.loadJson('localstorage.json');

        // Map danh sÃ¡ch lá»›p má»Ÿ Ä‘á»ƒ tra cá»©u nhanh (Key: course_id, Value: object lá»›p)
        const openClassesRaw = localData.courses_db_offline || [];
        const openClassesMap = new Map();
        openClassesRaw.forEach(c => openClassesMap.set(c.id, c));

        // 2. PhÃ¢n tÃ­ch Profile sinh viÃªn
        const { passed, failed, studying } = this.loader.getStudentStatus(localData);
        const graph = new PrerequisiteGraph(prereqs);

        // Set chá»©a cÃ¡c mÃ´n DE XUAT (dÃ¹ng Set Ä‘á»ƒ khÃ´ng trÃ¹ng láº·p)
        const rawRecommendations = new Set();

        // --- BÆ¯á»šC 1: Æ¯U TIÃŠN MÃ”N Ná»¢ (FAILED) ---
        console.log(""ğŸ” Äang quÃ©t mÃ´n ná»£..."");
        failed.forEach(cid => {
            const target = graph.findBlockingPrereq(cid, passed);
            // Náº¿u tÃ¬m Ä‘Æ°á»£c mÃ´n cáº§n há»c vÃ  mÃ´n Ä‘Ã³ KHÃ”NG Ä‘ang há»c
            if (target && !studying.has(target)) {
                rawRecommendations.add(target);
            }
        });

        // --- BÆ¯á»šC 2: Æ¯U TIÃŠN MÃ”N Báº®T BUá»˜C (MANDATORY) ---
        console.log(""ğŸ” Äang quÃ©t mÃ´n báº¯t buá»™c..."");
        coursesMeta.forEach(c => {
            const cid = c.course_id;
            // Logic: LÃ  mÃ´n BB + ChÆ°a Ä‘áº­u + KhÃ´ng Ä‘ang há»c
            if (c.course_type === 'BB' && !passed.has(cid) && !studying.has(cid)) {
                const target = graph.findBlockingPrereq(cid, passed);
                if (target && !passed.has(target) && !studying.has(target)) {
                    rawRecommendations.add(target);
                }
            }
        });

        // --- BÆ¯á»šC 3: MÃ”N Bá»” TRá»¢ (SOFT PREREQUISITES) - ""Xáº¢ LÃNG"" ---
        console.log(""ğŸ” Äang quÃ©t thÃªm cÃ¡c mÃ´n bá»• trá»£ (Xáº£ lÃ¡ng)..."");
        // Convert Set sang Array Ä‘á»ƒ duyá»‡t, trÃ¡nh lá»—i thay Ä‘á»•i Set khi Ä‘ang loop
        const currentCandidates = Array.from(rawRecommendations);

        currentCandidates.forEach(cid => {
            const softReqs = graph.softConstraints[cid] || [];
            softReqs.forEach(p => {
                if (!passed.has(p) && !rawRecommendations.has(p) && !studying.has(p)) {
                    // Kiá»ƒm tra mÃ´n bá»• trá»£ nÃ y cÃ³ Ä‘á»§ Ä‘iá»u kiá»‡n há»c khÃ´ng
                    const validP = graph.findBlockingPrereq(p, passed);
                    // Chá»‰ gá»£i Ã½ náº¿u chÃ­nh nÃ³ há»c Ä‘Æ°á»£c ngay (khÃ´ng bá»‹ dÃ¢y mÆ¡ rá»… mÃ¡)
                    if (validP === p) {
                        rawRecommendations.add(p);
                    }
                }
            });
        });

        // --- BÆ¯á»šC 4: KHá»šP Vá»šI Lá»ŠCH Má» Lá»šP (SCHEDULE CHECK) ---
        console.log(""ğŸ” Kiá»ƒm tra lá»‹ch má»Ÿ lá»›p ká»³ tá»›i..."");
        const finalOutput = [];

        // Sort cho Ä‘áº¹p Ä‘á»™i hÃ¬nh
        const sortedRecs = Array.from(rawRecommendations).sort();

        sortedRecs.forEach(cid => {
            if (openClassesMap.has(cid)) {
                // Láº¥y nguyÃªn object tá»« courses_db_offline Ä‘á»ƒ tráº£ vá» Ä‘Ãºng format
                finalOutput.push(openClassesMap.get(cid));
            } else {
                // console.log(`   -> Bá» qua ${cid}: Ká»³ nÃ y khÃ´ng má»Ÿ lá»›p.`);
            }
        });

        return finalOutput;
    }
}

// ==========================================
// 4. CHáº Y CHÆ¯Æ NG TRÃŒNH
// ==========================================
try {
    const app = new CourseRecommender();
    const result = app.run();

    // Xuáº¥t ra file
    const outputFilename = 'recommendation_result.json';
    fs.writeFileSync(outputFilename, JSON.stringify(result, null, 4), 'utf-8');

    console.log(`\nâœ… XONG! ÄÃ£ tÃ¬m tháº¥y ${result.length} mÃ´n há»c.`);
    console.log(`ğŸ‘‰ Káº¿t quáº£ Ä‘Ã£ lÆ°u vÃ o: ${outputFilename}`);

    // In thá»­ 2 káº¿t quáº£ Ä‘áº§u tiÃªn
    if (result.length > 0) {
        console.log(""\n--- Preview káº¿t quáº£ ---"");
        console.log(JSON.stringify(result.slice(0, 2), null, 2));
    } else {
        console.log(""âš ï¸ KhÃ´ng cÃ³ mÃ´n nÃ o phÃ¹ há»£p hoáº·c trÆ°á»ng khÃ´ng má»Ÿ lá»›p."");
    }

} catch (error) {
    console.error(""âŒ Lá»—i chÆ°Æ¡ng trÃ¬nh:"", error);

2026-01-08 19:14:08;Mai Quá»³nh Anh;"const fs = require('fs');
const path = require('path');

// ==========================================
// 1. DATA LOADER
// ==========================================
class DataLoader {
    constructor(dataDir = '.') {
        this.dataDir = dataDir;
    }

    loadJson(filename) {
        const filePath = path.join(this.dataDir, filename);
        if (!fs.existsSync(filePath)) return {};
        return JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(filePath, 'utf-8'));
    }

    getStudentStatus(localData) {
        const passed = new Set();
        const studying = new Set();
        // Map Ä‘á»ƒ lÆ°u sá»‘ tÃ­n chá»‰ cá»§a tá»«ng mÃ´n Ä‘Ã£ qua (Ä‘á»ƒ cá»™ng dá»“n)
        const passedCredits = new Map();

        const grades = localData?.student_db_full?.grades || [];

        grades.forEach(g => {
            const cid = g.id;
            let scoreRaw = g.score;
            // Parse credits tá»« string sang int (vd ""4"" -> 4)
            const credits = parseInt(g.credits) || 0;

            if (scoreRaw === """" || scoreRaw === ""(*)"" || scoreRaw == null) {
                studying.add(cid);
                return;
            }

            const score = parseFloat(scoreRaw);
            if (!isNaN(score) && score >= 5.0) {
                passed.add(cid);
                passedCredits.set(cid, credits);
            }
        });

        return { passed, studying, passedCredits };
    }
}

// ==========================================
// 2. GRAPH ENGINE (TiÃªn quyáº¿t)
// ==========================================
class PrerequisiteGraph {
    constructor(prereqData) {
        this.hardConstraints = {};
        this.softConstraints = {};
        this.buildGraph(prereqData);
    }

    buildGraph(data) {
        if (!Array.isArray(data)) return;
        data.forEach(item => {
            const cId = item.course_id;
            const pIds = item.prereq_id.replace(/,/g, ' ').split(/\s+/).filter(x => x.length > 0);

            pIds.forEach(pid => {
                if (item.type === 'PREVIOUS') {
                    if (!this.softConstraints[cId]) this.softConstraints[cId] = [];
                    this.softConstraints[cId].push(pid);
                } else {
                    if (!this.hardConstraints[cId]) this.hardConstraints[cId] = [];
                    this.hardConstraints[cId].push(pid);
                }
            });
        });
    }

    findBlockingPrereq(courseId, passedCourses) {
        if (passedCourses.has(courseId)) return null;
        const reqs = this.hardConstraints[courseId] || [];
        for (const req of reqs) {
            if (!passedCourses.has(req)) {
                return this.findBlockingPrereq(req, passedCourses) || req;
            }
        }
        return courseId;
    }
}

// ==========================================
// 3. RECOMMENDER CORE (Logic má»›i xá»­ lÃ½ Category)
// ==========================================
class CourseRecommender {
    constructor() {
        this.loader = new DataLoader();
    }

    /**
     * HÃ m kiá»ƒm tra má»™t nhÃ³m mÃ´n cá»¥ thá»ƒ (List IDs)
     * Tráº£ vá» danh sÃ¡ch cÃ¡c mÃ´n nÃªn há»c trong nhÃ³m Ä‘Ã³ náº¿u chÆ°a Ä‘á»§ tÃ­n chá»‰
     */
    checkGroupRequirement(groupTitle, requiredCredits, courseList, passed, passedCreditsMap, studying, graph, coursesMetaMap) {
        const recommendations = [];
        let currentCredits = 0;

        // 1. TÃ­nh tá»•ng tÃ­n chá»‰ Ä‘Ã£ Ä‘áº¡t trong nhÃ³m nÃ y
        courseList.forEach(cid => {
            if (passed.has(cid)) {
                // Láº¥y tÃ­n chá»‰ thá»±c táº¿ tá»« báº£ng Ä‘iá»ƒm hoáº·c tra cá»©u tá»« courses.json
                const cr = passedCreditsMap.get(cid) || coursesMetaMap.get(cid)?.credits || 0;
                currentCredits += cr;
            }
        });

        console.log(`   - NhÃ³m ""${groupTitle}"": ÄÃ£ Ä‘áº¡t ${currentCredits}/${requiredCredits} TC`);

        // 2. Náº¿u thiáº¿u tÃ­n chá»‰ -> Recommend cÃ¡c mÃ´n chÆ°a há»c trong nhÃ³m
        if (currentCredits < requiredCredits) {
            courseList.forEach(cid => {
                if (!passed.has(cid) && !studying.has(cid)) {
                    // Kiá»ƒm tra tiÃªn quyáº¿t trÆ°á»›c khi recommend
                    const target = graph.findBlockingPrereq(cid, passed);
                    if (target && !passed.has(target) && !studying.has(target)) {
                        recommendations.push(target);
                    }
                }
            });
        }
        return recommendations;
    }

    run() {
        console.log(""â³ Äang xá»­ lÃ½ dá»¯ liá»‡u..."");

        // Load Data
        const coursesMeta = this.loader.loadJson('courses.json');
        const categories = this.loader.loadJson('categories.json');
        const prereqs = this.loader.loadJson('prerequisites.json');
        const localData = this.loader.loadJson('localstorage.json');
        const openClassesRaw = localData.courses_db_offline || [];

        // Map data Ä‘á»ƒ tra cá»©u
        const coursesMetaMap = new Map();
        coursesMeta.forEach(c => coursesMetaMap.set(c.course_id, c));

        const openClassesMap = new Map();
        openClassesRaw.forEach(c => openClassesMap.set(c.id, c));

        const { passed, studying, passedCredits } = this.loader.getStudentStatus(localData);
        const graph = new PrerequisiteGraph(prereqs);
        const rawRecommendations = new Set();

        // --- QUÃ‰T CATEGORIES (LOGIC Má»šI Xá»¬ LÃ NOTE) ---
        console.log(""ğŸ” Kiá»ƒm tra tiáº¿n Ä‘á»™ theo nhÃ³m ngÃ nh..."");

        // HÃ m Ä‘á»‡ quy duyá»‡t cáº¥u trÃºc categories.json
        const traverseCategories = (obj) => {
            // TrÆ°á»ng há»£p 1: NhÃ³m cÃ³ 'sub_groups' (nhÆ° ToÃ¡n & Khoa há»c)
            if (obj.sub_groups) {
                obj.sub_groups.forEach(sub => {
                    const recs = this.checkGroupRequirement(
                        sub.title, sub.credits_required, sub.courses,
                        passed, passedCredits, studying, graph, coursesMetaMap
                    );
                    recs.forEach(r => rawRecommendations.add(r));
                });
            }
            // TrÆ°á»ng há»£p 2: NhÃ³m cÃ³ 'courses' trá»±c tiáº¿p (nhÆ° Social Economics cÅ©)
            else if (obj.courses && obj.credits_required) {
                const recs = this.checkGroupRequirement(
                    obj.title || ""NhÃ³m mÃ´n"", obj.credits_required, obj.courses,
                    passed, passedCredits, studying, graph, coursesMetaMap
                );
                recs.forEach(r => rawRecommendations.add(r));
            }
            // TrÆ°á»ng há»£p 3: Duyá»‡t tiáº¿p cÃ¡c object con (Ä‘á»‡ quy)
            else {
                for (const key in obj) {
                    if (typeof obj[key] === 'object' && obj[key] !== null) {
                        traverseCategories(obj[key]);
                    }
                }
            }
        };

        traverseCategories(categories);

        // --- Xá»¬ LÃ MÃ”N Bá»” TRá»¢ (SOFT PREREQ) ---
        console.log(""ğŸ” QuÃ©t thÃªm mÃ´n bá»• trá»£ (Xáº£ lÃ¡ng)..."");
        const currentCandidates = Array.from(rawRecommendations);
        currentCandidates.forEach(cid => {
            const softReqs = graph.softConstraints[cid] || [];
            softReqs.forEach(p => {
                if (!passed.has(p) && !rawRecommendations.has(p) && !studying.has(p)) {
                    const validP = graph.findBlockingPrereq(p, passed);
                    if (validP === p) rawRecommendations.add(p);
                }
            });
        });

        // --- KHá»šP Lá»ŠCH Má» Lá»šP ---
        console.log(""ğŸ” Khá»›p lá»‹ch má»Ÿ lá»›p..."");
        const finalOutput = [];
        Array.from(rawRecommendations).sort().forEach(cid => {
            if (openClassesMap.has(cid)) {
                finalOutput.push(openClassesMap.get(cid));
            }
        });

        return finalOutput;
    }
}

// CHáº Y
try {
    const app = new CourseRecommender();
    const result = app.run();
    const outputFilename = 'recommendation_result.json';
    fs.writeFileSync(outputFilename, JSON.stringify(result, null, 4), 'utf-8');
    console.log(`\nâœ… XONG! TÃ¬m tháº¥y ${result.length} mÃ´n.`);
    console.log(`ğŸ‘‰ Káº¿t quáº£: ${outputFilename}`);
} catch (e) {
    console.error(e);
}"

2026-01-09 20:07:07;Mai Quá»³nh Anh;"const fs = require('fs');
const path = require('path');

// ==========================================
// 1. DATA LOADER
// ==========================================
class DataLoader {
    constructor(dataDir = '.') {
        this.dataDir = dataDir;
    }

    loadJson(filename) {
        const filePath = path.join(this.dataDir, filename);
        if (!fs.existsSync(filePath)) return filename === 'courses.json' ? [] : {};
        return JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(filePath, 'utf-8'));
    }

    getStudentStatus(localData) {
        const passed = new Set();
        const studying = new Set();
        const failed = new Set();
        const passedCreditsMap = new Map();

        const grades = localData?.student_db_full?.grades || [];

        grades.forEach(g => {
            const cid = g.id;
            let scoreRaw = g.score;
            const credits = parseInt(g.credits) || 0;

            if (scoreRaw === """" || scoreRaw === ""(*)"" || scoreRaw == null) {
                studying.add(cid);
                return;
            }

            const score = parseFloat(scoreRaw);
            if (!isNaN(score)) {
                if (score >= 5.0) {
                    passed.add(cid);
                    passedCreditsMap.set(cid, credits);
                } else {
                    failed.add(cid);
                }
            } else {
                studying.add(cid);
            }
        });

        return { passed, failed, studying, passedCreditsMap };
    }
}

// ==========================================
// 2. GRAPH ENGINE
// ==========================================
class PrerequisiteGraph {
    constructor(prereqData) {
        this.hardConstraints = {};
        this.softConstraints = {};
        this.buildGraph(prereqData);
    }

    buildGraph(data) {
        if (!Array.isArray(data)) return;
        data.forEach(item => {
            const cId = item.course_id;
            const pIds = item.prereq_id.replace(/,/g, ' ').split(/\s+/).filter(x => x.length > 0);

            pIds.forEach(pid => {
                if (item.type === 'PREVIOUS') {
                    if (!this.softConstraints[cId]) this.softConstraints[cId] = [];
                    this.softConstraints[cId].push(pid);
                } else {
                    if (!this.hardConstraints[cId]) this.hardConstraints[cId] = [];
                    this.hardConstraints[cId].push(pid);
                }
            });
        });
    }

    findBlockingPrereq(courseId, passedCourses) {
        if (passedCourses.has(courseId)) return null;
        const reqs = this.hardConstraints[courseId] || [];
        for (const req of reqs) {
            if (!passedCourses.has(req)) {
                return this.findBlockingPrereq(req, passedCourses) || req;
            }
        }
        return courseId;
    }
}

// ==========================================
// 3. RECOMMENDER CORE
// ==========================================
class CourseRecommender {
    constructor() {
        this.loader = new DataLoader();
        // Map lÆ°u káº¿t quáº£: Key = CourseID, Value = status_code (String)
        this.recommendationsMap = new Map();
    }

    addRec(id, status) {
        const priorities = {
            'RETAKE': 4,
            'MANDATORY': 3,
            'ELECTIVE_REQUIRED': 2,
            'SUGGESTED': 1
        };

        if (this.recommendationsMap.has(id)) {
            const currentStatus = this.recommendationsMap.get(id);
            // Náº¿u tráº¡ng thÃ¡i má»›i quan trá»ng hÆ¡n tráº¡ng thÃ¡i cÅ© thÃ¬ ghi Ä‘Ã¨
            if (priorities[status] > priorities[currentStatus]) {
                this.recommendationsMap.set(id, status);
            }
        } else {
            this.recommendationsMap.set(id, status);
        }
    }

    checkGroupRequirement(requiredCredits, courseList, passed, passedCreditsMap, studying, graph, coursesMetaMap) {
        let currentCredits = 0;
        courseList.forEach(cid => {
            if (passed.has(cid)) {
                const cr = passedCreditsMap.get(cid) || coursesMetaMap.get(cid)?.credits || 0;
                currentCredits += cr;
            }
        });

        if (currentCredits < requiredCredits) {
            courseList.forEach(cid => {
                if (!passed.has(cid) && !studying.has(cid)) {
                    const target = graph.findBlockingPrereq(cid, passed);
                    if (target && !passed.has(target) && !studying.has(target)) {
                        this.addRec(target, 'ELECTIVE_REQUIRED');
                    }
                }
            });
        }
    }

    run() {
        console.log(""â³ Äang xá»­ lÃ½ dá»¯ liá»‡u..."");

        const coursesMeta = this.loader.loadJson('courses.json');
        const categories = this.loader.loadJson('categories.json');
        const prereqs = this.loader.loadJson('prerequisites.json');
        const localData = this.loader.loadJson('localstorage.json');
        const openClassesRaw = localData.courses_db_offline || [];

        const coursesMetaMap = new Map();
        coursesMeta.forEach(c => coursesMetaMap.set(c.course_id, c));

        const openClassesMap = new Map();
        openClassesRaw.forEach(c => openClassesMap.set(c.id, c));

        const { passed, failed, studying, passedCreditsMap } = this.loader.getStudentStatus(localData);
        const graph = new PrerequisiteGraph(prereqs);

        // 1. MÃ”N Rá»šT (RETAKE)
        failed.forEach(cid => {
            const target = graph.findBlockingPrereq(cid, passed);
            if (target && !studying.has(target)) {
                this.addRec(target, 'RETAKE');
            }
        });

        // 2. MÃ”N Báº®T BUá»˜C (MANDATORY)
        coursesMeta.forEach(c => {
            const cid = c.course_id;
            if (c.course_type === 'BB' && !passed.has(cid) && !studying.has(cid)) {
                const target = graph.findBlockingPrereq(cid, passed);
                if (target && !passed.has(target) && !studying.has(target)) {
                    this.addRec(target, 'MANDATORY');
                }
            }
        });

        // 3. NHÃ“M NGÃ€NH (ELECTIVE_REQUIRED)
        const traverseCategories = (obj) => {
            if (obj.sub_groups) {
                obj.sub_groups.forEach(sub => {
                    this.checkGroupRequirement(
                        sub.credits_required, sub.courses,
                        passed, passedCreditsMap, studying, graph, coursesMetaMap
                    );
                });
            } else if (obj.courses && obj.credits_required) {
                this.checkGroupRequirement(
                    obj.credits_required, obj.courses,
                    passed, passedCreditsMap, studying, graph, coursesMetaMap
                );
            } else {
                for (const key in obj) {
                    if (typeof obj[key] === 'object' && obj[key] !== null) {
                        traverseCategories(obj[key]);
                    }
                }
            }
        };
        traverseCategories(categories);

        // 4. MÃ”N Bá»” TRá»¢ (SUGGESTED)
        const currentIds = Array.from(this.recommendationsMap.keys());
        currentIds.forEach(cid => {
            const softReqs = graph.softConstraints[cid] || [];
            softReqs.forEach(p => {
                if (!passed.has(p) && !this.recommendationsMap.has(p) && !studying.has(p)) {
                    const validP = graph.findBlockingPrereq(p, passed);
                    if (validP === p) {
                        this.addRec(p, 'SUGGESTED');
                    }
                }
            });
        });

        // 5. OUTPUT
        console.log(""ğŸ” Khá»›p lá»‹ch má»Ÿ lá»›p..."");
        const finalOutput = [];

        // Sort theo Ä‘á»™ Æ°u tiÃªn: RETAKE > MANDATORY > ELECTIVE > SUGGESTED
        const sortedRecs = Array.from(this.recommendationsMap.entries()).sort((a, b) => {
            const priority = { 'RETAKE': 4, 'MANDATORY': 3, 'ELECTIVE_REQUIRED': 2, 'SUGGESTED': 1 };
            return priority[b[1]] - priority[a[1]];
        });

        sortedRecs.forEach(([cid, statusCode]) => {
            if (openClassesMap.has(cid)) {
                const classData = openClassesMap.get(cid);
                finalOutput.push({
                    ...classData,
                    status_code: statusCode // Chá»‰ giá»¯ láº¡i mÃ£ status
                });
            }
        });

        return finalOutput;
    }
}

// CHáº Y
try {
    const app = new CourseRecommender();
    const result = app.run();
    const outputFilename = 'recommendation_result.json';
    fs.writeFileSync(outputFilename, JSON.stringify(result, null, 4), 'utf-8');

    console.log(`\nâœ… XONG! TÃ¬m tháº¥y ${result.length} mÃ´n.`);
    console.log(`ğŸ‘‰ Káº¿t quáº£: ${outputFilename}`);

    // Preview 1 dÃ²ng
    if (result.length > 0) {
        console.log(""VÃ­ dá»¥ káº¿t quáº£:"");
        console.log(JSON.stringify(result[0], null, 2));
    }

} catch (e) {
    console.error(e);
}"
